---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-indigo-950 text-white w-full">
    <canvas id="canvas-particles" class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></canvas>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950/20 via-indigo-950/80 to-indigo-950"></div>

    <div class="relative z-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center px-4 md:px-6 w-full flex flex-col items-center">
        
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm animate-fade-in">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-indigo-300">Derecho de Familia • CABA</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-12 w-full">
            <span class="block">ABOGADOS</span>
            
            <div class="relative h-[1.2em] md:h-[1em] mt-2 flex justify-center items-center">
                <span class="word-fade animate-fade-1 text-amber-400">Divorcio Express</span>
                <span class="word-fade animate-fade-2 text-amber-400">Cuidado Personal</span>
                <span class="word-fade animate-fade-3 text-amber-400">División de Bienes</span>
                <span class="word-fade animate-fade-4 text-amber-400 text-fluid-long">Compensación Económica</span>
            </div>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-indigo-100/70 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium px-4">
            Atención jurídica estratégica y reserva absoluta en procesos de alta complejidad. <span class="text-white font-bold">Tu voz cuenta.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center w-full px-6">
            <a href="https://wa.me/5491141689773" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-white text-indigo-950 rounded-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-indigo-400 hover:text-white transition-all shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 1 1-7.6-11.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8.9L21 3z"></path></svg>
                Consulta Privada
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    // Tu script de partículas se mantiene igual...
</script>

<style>
    .word-fade {
        position: absolute;
        opacity: 0;
        width: 100%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        white-space: nowrap;
        transform: translate3d(0, 15px, 0);
        will-change: transform, opacity;
    }

    /* Tipografía fluida para la frase más larga */
    .text-fluid-long {
        /* Se adapta entre 1.8rem y el tamaño original según el ancho de pantalla */
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 7.5vw, 1em);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .text-fluid-long {
            font-size: 6.2vw; /* Ajuste fino para pantallas muy pequeñas (iPhone SE) */
        }
    }

    @keyframes wordAnimation {
        0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(0, 15px, 0); }
        5% { opacity: 1; transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); }
        20% { opacity: 1; transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); }
        25% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(0, -15px, 0); }
        100% { opacity: 0; }
    }

    .animate-fade-1 { animation: wordAnimation 8s infinite 0s; }
    .animate-fade-2 { animation: wordAnimation 8s infinite 2s; }
    .animate-fade-3 { animation: wordAnimation 8s infinite 4s; }
    .animate-fade-4 { animation: wordAnimation 8s infinite 6s; }

    .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
</style>